om/blog/2015/03/react.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 154, 97); text-decoration: none; transition: background-color 0.2s ease, border 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease-in-out, outline 0.2s ease; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 154, 97, 0.247059); padding-bottom: 1px;\">React 入门实例教程</a></li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">React 起源于 Facebook 的内部项目，因为该公司对市场上所有 JavaScript MVC 框架，都不满意，就决定自己写一套，用来架设&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 154, 97); text-decoration: none; transition: background-color 0.2s ease, border 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease-in-out, outline 0.2s ease; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 154, 97, 0.247059); padding-bottom: 1px;\">Instagram</a>&nbsp;的网站。做出来以后，发现这套东西很好用，就在2013年5月开源了。</p><h2 id=\"articleHeader2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-rendering: auto; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); padding-bottom: 10px;\">什么是React</h2><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 1.5em 0px 1.5em 3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">A JAVASCRIPT LIBRARY FOR BUILDING USER INTERFACES</p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 3em;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\">用来构建UI的 JavaScript库</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\">React 不是一个 MVC 框架，仅仅是视图（V）层的库</li></ul></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\"><a href=\"https://facebook.github.io/react/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 154, 97); text-decoration: none; transition: background-color 0.2s ease, border 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease-in-out, outline 0.2s ease; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 154, 97, 0.247059); padding-bottom: 1px;\">React 官网</a></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\"><a href=\"https://doc.react-china.org/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 154, 97); text-decoration: none; transition: background-color 0.2s ease, border 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease-in-out, outline 0.2s ease; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 154, 97, 0.247059); padding-bottom: 1px;\">React 中文文档</a></li></ul><h3 id=\"articleHeader3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.25em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-rendering: auto; font-size: 1.5em;\">特点</h3><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 1.5em 0px 1.5em 3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\">1 使用 JSX语法 创建组件，实现组件化开发，<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">为函数式的 UI 编程方式打开了大门</strong></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\">2 性能高的让人称赞：通过&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.93em; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border: 1px solid rgb(225, 225, 232); white-space: nowrap;\">diff算法</code>&nbsp;和&nbsp;<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.93em; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border: 1px solid rgb(225, 225, 232); white-space: nowrap;\">虚拟DOM</code>&nbsp;实现视图的高效更新</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\">3 HTML仅仅是个开始</li></ul><pre class=\"hljs haml\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 1em; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.93em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; line-height: 1.45; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; border: none; overflow: auto; max-height: 35em; position: relative; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><code class=\"html\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; color: inherit; border-radius: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; white-space: inherit; overflow-wrap: normal;\">&gt; JSX --TO--&gt; EveryThing  -<span class=\"ruby\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> JSX --&gt; HTML </span>-<span class=\"ruby\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> JSX --&gt; native ios或android中的组件（XML） </span>-<span class=\"ruby\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> JSX --&gt; VR </span>-<span class=\"ruby\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> JSX --&gt; 物联网</span></code></pre><h2 id=\"articleHeader4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-rendering: auto; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); padding-bottom: 10px;\">为什么要用React</h2><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 1.5em 0px 1.5em 3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\">1 使用<code style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 2px 4px; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.93em; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); border-radius: 4px; background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); border: 1px solid rgb(225, 225, 232); white-space: nowrap;\">组件化</code>开发方式，符合现代Web开发的趋势</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\">2 技术成熟，社区完善，配件齐全，适用于大型Web项目（生态系统健全）</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\">3 由Facebook专门的团队维护，技术支持可靠</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\">4 ReactNative - Learn once, write anywhere: Build mobile apps with React</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\">5 使用方式简单，性能非常高，支持服务端渲染</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\">6 React非常火，从技术角度，可以满足好奇心，提高技术水平；从职业角度，有利于求职和晋升，有利于参与潜力大的项目</li></ul><h2 id=\"articleHeader5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-rendering: auto; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); padding-bottom: 10px;\">React中的核心概念</h2><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 1.5em 0px 1.5em 3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\">1 虚拟DOM（Virtual DOM）</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\">2 Diff算法（虚拟DOM的加速器，提升React性能的法宝）</li></ul><h2 id=\"articleHeader6\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-rendering: auto; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); padding-bottom: 10px;\">虚拟DOM（Vitural DOM）</h2><blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 1.5em 0px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(0, 154, 97); background: rgb(246, 246, 246); font-style: italic; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;\">React将DOM抽象为虚拟DOM，虚拟DOM其实就是用一个对象来描述DOM，通过对比前后两个对象的差异，最终只把变化的部分重新渲染，提高渲染的效率<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25px;\">为什么用虚拟dom，当dom反生更改时需要遍历 而原生dom可遍历属性多大231个 且大部分与渲染无关 更新页面代价太大</p></blockquote><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 1.5em 0px 1.5em 3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/livoras/blog/issues/13\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 154, 97); text-decoration: none; transition: background-color 0.2s ease, border 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease-in-out, outline 0.2s ease; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 154, 97, 0.247059); padding-bottom: 1px;\">如何实现一个 Virtual DOM 算法</a></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\"><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/31809713\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 154, 97); text-decoration: none; transition: background-color 0.2s ease, border 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease-in-out, outline 0.2s ease; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 154, 97, 0.247059); padding-bottom: 1px;\">理解 Virtual DOM</a></li></ul><h3 id=\"articleHeader7\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.25em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-rendering: auto; font-size: 1.5em;\">VituralDOM的处理方式</h3><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 1.5em 0px 1.5em 3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\">1 用 JavaScript 对象结构表示 DOM 树的结构，然后用这个树构建一个真正的 DOM 树，插到文档当中</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\">2 当状态变更的时候，重新构造一棵新的对象树。然后用新的树和旧的树进行比较，记录两棵树差异</li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\">3 把2所记录的差异应用到步骤1所构建的真正的DOM树上，视图就更新了</li></ul><h2 id=\"articleHeader8\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.5em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-rendering: auto; font-size: 1.75em; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); padding-bottom: 10px;\">Diff算法</h2><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 1.5em 0px 1.5em 3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\"><a href=\"https://facebook.github.io/react/docs/reconciliation.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 154, 97); text-decoration: none; transition: background-color 0.2s ease, border 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease-in-out, outline 0.2s ease; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 154, 97, 0.247059); padding-bottom: 1px;\">Reconciliation diff</a></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\"><a href=\"https://doc.react-china.org/docs/reconciliation.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 154, 97); text-decoration: none; transition: background-color 0.2s ease, border 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease-in-out, outline 0.2s ease; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 154, 97, 0.247059); padding-bottom: 1px;\">diff算法 - 中文文档</a></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/20346379\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 154, 97); text-decoration: none; transition: background-color 0.2s ease, border 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease-in-out, outline 0.2s ease; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 154, 97, 0.247059); padding-bottom: 1px;\">不可思议的 react diff</a></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/zmmbreeze/blog/issues/9\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 154, 97); text-decoration: none; transition: background-color 0.2s ease, border 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, opacity 0.2s ease-in-out, outline 0.2s ease; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; outline: 0px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 154, 97, 0.247059); padding-bottom: 1px;\">React diff 算法</a></li></ul><blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 10px 20px; margin: 1.5em 0px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(0, 154, 97); background: rgb(246, 246, 246); font-style: italic; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;\">当你使用React的时候，在某个时间点 render() 函数创建了一棵React元素树，<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />在下一个state或者props更新的时候，render() 函数将创建一棵新的React元素树，<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />React将对比这两棵树的不同之处，计算出如何高效的更新UI（只更新变化的地方）</blockquote><pre class=\"hljs xml\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 1em; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.93em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; line-height: 1.45; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; border: none; overflow: auto; max-height: 35em; position: relative; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><code class=\"html\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; color: inherit; border-radius: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; white-space: inherit; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 136);\">&lt;!-- 了解：  有一些解决将一棵树转换为另一棵树的最小操作数算法问题的通用方案。然而，树中元素个数为n，最先进的算法 的时间复杂度为O(n3) 。 如果直接使用这个算法，在React中展示1000个元素则需要进行10亿次的比较。这操作太过昂贵，相反，React基于两点假设，实现了一个O(n)算法，提升性能： --&gt;</span></code></pre><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 1.5em 0px 1.5em 3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px;\">React中有两种假定：</p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 0px 3em;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\">1&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">两个不同类型的元素会产生不同的树(根元素不同结构树一定不同)</strong></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\">2&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">开发者可以通过key属性指定不同树中没有发生改变的子元素</strong></li></ul></li></ul><h3 id=\"articleHeader9\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.25em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-rendering: auto; font-size: 1.5em;\">Diff算法的说明 - 1</h3><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 1.5em 0px 1.5em 3em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 20px; margin: 0.3em 0px;\">如果两棵树的根元素类型不同，React会销毁旧树，创建新树</li></ul><pre class=\"hljs dts\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 1em; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 0.93em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 1.5em; line-height: 1.45; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; border: none; overflow: auto; max-height: 35em; position: relative; margin-top: 0px !important;\"><code class=\"js\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Source Code Pro&quot;, Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace; font-size: 1em; color: inherit; border-radius: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; white-space: inherit; overflow-wrap: normal;\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 136);\">// 旧树</span> <span class=\"hljs-params\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&lt;div&gt;</span>   <span class=\"hljs-params\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&lt;Counter /&gt;</span> <span class=\"hljs-params\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&lt;/div&gt;</span>  <span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(153, 153, 136);\">// 新树</span> <span class=\"hljs-params\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&lt;span&gt;</span>   <span class=\"hljs-params\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&lt;Counter /&gt;</span> <span class=\"hljs-params\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&lt;/span&gt;</span>  执行过程：destory Counter -&gt; insert Counter</code></pre><h3 id=\"articleHeader10\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1